headline: 4 Solar Stocks That Might Beat the Market in 2025
summary: Global solar installations are estimated to fall 0.4% from the year-earlier level to 492 gigawatts in 2025. Yet, you can keep FSLR, ENPH, NXT and CSIQ on the watchlist.
